<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٧٠٥ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4869">عَمْرُو بْنُ عَلِيٍّ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6217">مُعَاذُ بْنُ مُعَاذٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3834">ابْنُ عَوْنٍ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5159">الْقَاسِمِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3026">أُمِّ الْمُؤْمِنِينَ </a><span class="special">﵂</span> قَالَتْ: <span class="c2">«فَتَلْتُ قَلَائِدَهَا مِنْ عِهْنٍ كَانَ عِنْدِي.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>